init_text:
A woman has been dating guy after guy, but it never seems to work out. She’s unaware that she’s actually been dating the same guy over and over; a shapeshifter who’s fallen for her, and is certain he’s going to get it right this time.

One day,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: she meets a guy who seems different from the rest, and she can’t help but be drawn to him.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They go out on a date, and the woman is surprised to find that Pog is nothing like the other guys she's dated.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He knows that he has to tell her the truth about himself, but he doesn't want to lose her.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He tells her that he is a shapeshifter, and that he has been with many women in the past.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Sara is shocked, but she is not completely freaked out by this.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She tells him that she understands.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Poc and Sara fall in love and get married.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They have a wonderful life together.
